text: Helmut Hartmann (born 2 February 1936) is a German equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:German male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of East Germany Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Damme
